(__WEBPACK_DEFAULT_EXPORT__)\n/* harmony export */ });\n/**\n * Throttle decorator\n * @param {Function} fn\n * @param {Number} freq\n * @return {Function}\n */\nfunction throttle(fn, freq) {\n  let clearTimeout(timer);\n      timer = null;\n    }\n    fn.apply(null, args);\n  }\n\n  const throttled = (...args) => {\n    const now = Date.now();\n    const passed = now - timestamp;\n    if (
